NERSC Cori is a Cray sytem.
Before compiling dftfe or the required libraries do:

export XTPE_LINK_TYPE=dynamic
export CRAYPE_LINK_TYPE=dynamic
module swap craype-haswell craype-mic-knl
module load craype-hugepages2M

Recommeneded to put the above in your bash script (except module swap craype-haswell craype-mic-knl)
